The '''Philippines national under-23 football team''' (also known as the '''Philippines Olympic team''') represents the [[Philippines]] in international [[association football|football]] competitions in the [[Football at the Summer Olympics|Olympic Games]], [[Football at the Asian Games|Asian Games]], [[Football at the Southeast Asian Games|Southeast Asian Games]] and any other under-23 international football tournaments.  It is controlled by the [[Philippine Football Federation]], the governing body of football in the country.

